    "Id": "chassisdef_karura_KAU-5RA",
    "Name": "Karura",
    "Details": "The Karura is fast and versatile, able to lead assaults or reinforce battle lines with ease. Its solid armor provides good protection, though it lacks effective weapons beyond 450 meters. However, its above-average speed compensates for this limitation. Armed with a powerful Heavy PPC, two Medium Lasers, and CASE-protected Streak SRM 6 launchers, the Karura delivers accurate and reliable firepower. This balanced combination of speed, armor, and weaponry ensures the Karura remains a durable and dependable presence on the battlefield.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - PPC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
